headline: Jabil Declares Quarterly Dividend
summary: ST. PETERSBURG, Fla., April 16, 2025--Jabil Inc. (NYSE: JBL) announced that its Board of Directors declared a quarterly dividend of $0.08 per share of common stock to shareholders of record as of May 15, 2025. The dividend is payable on June 3, 2025.
